    "In addition, these surfaces generate minimal capillary forces, limiting their ability to trap large MPs from flowing aqueous solutions.",
    "Researchers have made microfabricated quasi-3D plasmonic optical grating structures with features in the same order as the SERS excitation wavelength 13.",
    "However, these methods are unsuitable for MPs > 1 μm, which is more typical in waterbourne particles and would still require PCPT methods for complex samples.",
